house. He grabbed at the man, but the man pushed his way into the
house, McCarty said.
   The woman who owns the house said the stranger ran through
several rooms before charging up a staircase and into her
20-year-old son's room. The startled resident looked on as police
pulled the man out of bed.
   The man was arrested on a charge of burglary because he entered
the home without permission, McCarty said.
